2. cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) - The paper proposes new tight bounds for the generalized Marcum and Nuttall Q-functions, which involves numerical analysis and optimization techniques.
3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper mentions the application of the proposed bounds in wireless sensor networks, which is a topic related to social and information networks.
4. cs.MS (Mathematical Software) - The paper involves mathematical computations and the development of new bounds, which may require the use of mathematical software.
5. cs.SP (Signal Processing) - The paper mentions the extraction of the log-likelihood ratio for differential phase-shift keying (DPSK) signals, which is a topic related to signal processing.
